Local Functions (/std/inheritables/living.c)

int query_base_stat(string stat);

Returns the value of a stat.  This not does include any bonuses which may be placed on the stat due to armour, magic or other items.

See also: set_stats(), set_stat(), query_stats(), query_stat(), query_base_stat(), set_stat_bonuses(), set_stat_bonus(), add_stat_bonus(), query_stat_bonus()
